# lang attribute. The choice of language is intentional since English is
# never written in Han script.
<span font="Cantarell 11" fallback="false">Englishๆผขๅญ—English<span lang="en-us">ๆผขๅญ—</span>Englishๆผข<span lang="en-us">ๆผขๅญ—</span>ๅญ—</span>
